sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Director as Director
    participant Sequence as LandingSequence
    participant Bus as AnimationBus
    participant Hero as Hero
    participant Work as Work
    participant Bio as Biography
    participant DOM as DOM

    Note over Director,DOM: Initialization Phase

    Director->>+Sequence: new LandingSequence(bus, sections)
    Sequence->>Sequence: Store bus reference
    Sequence->>Sequence: Store sections (hero, work, biography)
    Sequence->>Sequence: Initialize state (isStarted: false)
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note over Sequence,Bus: Setup Event Listeners (setupSequence)
    
    Sequence->>+Bus: on('section:main-header:intro:complete')
    Note right of Bus: Listener 1: Hero complete → Work intro
    Bus-->>-Sequence: unsubscribe function
    
    Sequence->>+Bus: on('section:main-header:scroll:exit')
    Note right of Bus: Listener 2: Hero exit → Biography intro
    Bus-->>-Sequence: unsubscribe function
    
    Sequence->>+Bus: on('section:work:scroll:enter')
    Note right of Bus: Listener 3: Work enters viewport
    Bus-->>-Sequence: unsubscribe function
    
    Sequence->>+Bus: on('section:biography:scroll:enter')
    Note right of Bus: Listener 4: Biography enters → fade overlay
    Bus-->>-Sequence: unsubscribe function
    
    Sequence->>+Bus: on('section:biography:intro:complete')
    Note right of Bus: Listener 5: Mark sequence complete
    Bus-->>-Sequence: unsubscribe function
    end
    
    Sequence-->>-Director: LandingSequence ready
    Note right of Sequence: Event listeners active,<br/>waiting for events

    Note over Director,DOM: Sequence Execution

    Director->>+Sequence: start()
    Sequence->>Sequence: Set isStarted = true
    Sequence->>+Hero: playIntro()
    Note right of Hero: TextParty.roll animation begins
    Hero->>Hero: Animate title entrance
    
    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
    Note over Hero,Work: Step 1: Hero Intro → Work Intro
    Hero->>+Bus: emit('section:main-header:intro:complete')
    Bus->>Bus: Trigger registered listeners
    Bus->>-Sequence: Event: intro:complete
    activate Sequence
    Note right of Sequence: Listener 1 triggered
    Sequence->>+Work: playIntro()
    Work->>Work: Fade in work section
    Work->>Work: Show printer marks
    Work->>+Bus: emit('section:work:intro:complete')
    Bus-->>-Work: Event dispatched
    deactivate Work
    deactivate Sequence
    end
    
    Note over Hero,DOM: User Scrolls Down
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over Hero,Bio: Step 2: Hero Scroll Exit → Biography Intro
    Hero->>Hero: Scroll trigger activated
    Hero->>+Bus: emit('section:main-header:scroll:exit')
    Bus->>-Sequence: Event: scroll:exit
    activate Sequence
    Note right of Sequence: Listener 2 triggered
    Sequence->>+Bio: playIntro()
    Bio->>Bio: Fade in biography section
    Bio->>Bio: Prepare list items
    Bio->>+Bus: emit('section:biography:intro:complete')
    Bus->>-Sequence: Event: intro:complete
    activate Sequence
    Note right of Sequence: Listener 5 triggered
    Sequence->>Sequence: Set isComplete = true
    deactivate Sequence
    deactivate Bio
    deactivate Sequence
    end
    
    Note over Work,DOM: User Continues Scrolling
    
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
    Note over Work,Bio: Step 3: Work Scroll Enter
    Work->>Work: ScrollTrigger onEnter
    Work->>+Bus: emit('section:work:scroll:enter')
    Bus->>-Sequence: Event: scroll:enter
    activate Sequence
    Note right of Sequence: Listener 3 triggered<br/>(printer marks already visible)
    deactivate Sequence
    end
    
    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
    Note over Bio,DOM: Step 4: Biography Scroll Enter
    Bio->>Bio: ScrollTrigger onEnter
    Bio->>+Bus: emit('section:biography:scroll:enter')
    Bus->>-Sequence: Event: scroll:enter
    activate Sequence
    Note right of Sequence: Listener 4 triggered
    Sequence->>+DOM: getElementById('overlay-primary')
    DOM-->>-Sequence: overlay element
    Sequence->>DOM: gsap.to(overlay, opacity: 0.5)
    Note right of DOM: Fade overlay for<br/>reading experience
    deactivate Sequence
    end
    
    deactivate Hero
    deactivate Sequence
    
    Note over Director,DOM: Sequence Complete

    alt Cleanup Required
        Director->>+Sequence: destroy()
        Sequence->>Sequence: Call all unsubscribe functions
        Sequence->>Bus: Remove all event listeners
        Sequence->>Sequence: Clear references (bus, sections)
        Sequence-->>-Director: Cleanup complete
    end

    Note over Director,DOM: LandingSequence Active
